roleset.name: induced by a doctor's words or actions

example.name: iatrogenic-j
example.text: Many biological psychiatrists who base their practices around medication management will tell you the condition does n't exist , or that if it exists it is " iatrogenic , " meaning it is caused by therapists training their patients to interpret their symptoms as if they have a whole set of distinct personalities .
